cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.SY

The paper presents a new training algorithm for reinforcement learning problems using neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm also employs optimization techniques (cs.NE) and is applied to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY) through the pole balancing problem.
